{"id": 1776, "genre": 1002, "title": "你真的是一个“自己说了算”的人吗？", "description": "选关东煮都要挑挑拣拣三思而后行 or 挑大学都只要一瞬间，哪个是你？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 24857, "comment_count": 51, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170705151239KkVRSAcupg4xCqhG.png", "page_style": 0, "question_style": 1, "category": 4, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-16T02:48:31Z", "column": null, "gender_question": {"id": 2536, "content": "你的性别是：", "genre": 4, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 218644, "title": "男", "content": "", "image": null}, {"id": 218646, "title": "女", "content": "", "image": null}], "image": null}, "slide_question": {"id": 2537, "content": "你觉得自己做决定的风格更倾向于：", "genre": 3, "position": 2, "max_score": 10.0, "options": [{"id": 218648, "title": "超有主见", "content": "拍板就在一瞬间！", "image": null}, {"id": 218649, "title": "动摇星人", "content": "再给我两分钟想！", "image": null}], "image": null}, "normal_questions": [{"id": 2538, "content": "只是想去剪个头发，理发师说烫/染一下效果更好，你曾经被说动过吗？", "genre": 1, "position": 3, "options": [{"id": 218650, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 31, "image": "img/option/option/201707061944259VcxWdrL3wqU4eHf.gif"}, {"id": 218651, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 69, "image": "img/option/option/20170706194217OKdFUP9ErZk4sX6l.gif"}], "image": null}, {"id": 2539, "content": "便利店想买杯水，被问要不要+3元换购价值6元的零食，你会：", "genre": 1, "position": 4, "options": [{"id": 218652, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 22, "image": "img/option/option/20170706194444VEorMNants4qchev.gif"}, {"id": 218653, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 78, "image": "img/option/option/20170706194756U7GfPhu1YopKQC8D.gif"}], "image": null}, {"id": 2540, "content": "在便利店买饮料小吃的你更像是：", "genre": 1, "position": 5, "options": [{"id": 218949, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 20, "image": "img/option/option/20170704151049hu9FcC0ypHGjT2YS.png"}, {"id": 218950, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 80, "image": "img/option/option/20170704151102rUX0NVKmWY4MuJv8.png"}], "image": null}, {"id": 2541, "content": "